openapi: "3.0.0"
servers:
  - url: http://localhost:8080/api
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Gaming News API
paths:
  /news:
    summary: Get list of latest gaming news
    get:
      tags:
        - News
      summary: Get list of latest gaming news
      operationId: getNews
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Expected response to a valid request
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/ArticleList"

components:
  schemas:
    ArticleList:
      type: array
      items:
        $ref: "#/components/schema/Article"
    Article:
      required:
        - id
        - title
        - date
        - description
        - imageUrl
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
        title:
          type: string
        date:
          type: string
          format: date
        description:
          type: string
        imageUrl:
          type: string
